<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>linux on ⚝</title><link>/tags/linux/</link><description>Recent content in linux on ⚝</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 Aug 2021 17:50:26 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/tags/linux/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Linux Top命令</title><link>/post/linux-top%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</link><pubDate>Sun, 22 Aug 2021 17:50:26 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/linux-top%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;code>top&lt;/code>命令用于Linux系统资源监控。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Linux ps命令</title><link>/post/linux-ps%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</link><pubDate>Sun, 22 Aug 2021 17:48:55 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/linux-ps%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;code>ps&lt;/code>命令显示正在运行进程的快照。如果要实时显示正在运行的进程，请使用&lt;code>top&lt;/code>命令。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Linux资源限制</title><link>/post/linux%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6/</link><pubDate>Sun, 22 Aug 2021 17:43:06 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/linux%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6/</guid><description>&lt;p>了解Linux资源限制对系统配置和优化有帮助.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Linux挂载硬盘</title><link>/post/linux%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98/</link><pubDate>Sat, 17 Jul 2021 09:47:47 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/linux%E6%8C%82%E8%BD%BD%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98/</guid><description>&lt;p>linux挂载硬盘和lvm相关了解。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>dirname和basename</title><link>/post/dirname%E5%92%8Cbasename/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Jul 2021 19:42:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/dirname%E5%92%8Cbasename/</guid><description>&lt;p>从路径获取目录部分或文件名部分可以分别使用&lt;code>dirname&lt;/code>和&lt;code>basename&lt;/code>命令。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Process Substitution 进程替换</title><link>/post/process-substitution-%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Jul 2021 14:39:29 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/process-substitution-%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E6%9B%BF%E6%8D%A2/</guid><description>&lt;p>进程替换是一种重定向形式，其中进程的输入或输出（某些命令序列）作为临时文件出现。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Bash One Liners 3 重定向相关翻译与理解</title><link>/post/bash-one-liners-3-%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91%E4%B8%8E%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Jul 2021 14:25:39 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/bash-one-liners-3-%E9%87%8D%E5%AE%9A%E5%90%91%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91%E4%B8%8E%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3/</guid><description>&lt;p>重定向其实是通过操作&lt;strong>文件描述符&lt;/strong>来完成的，这样会更容易理解。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>配置sftp</title><link>/post/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEsftp/</link><pubDate>Sun, 11 Apr 2021 16:49:23 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEsftp/</guid><description>&lt;p>sftp采用的是ssh加密隧道，安装性方面较ftp强，而且依赖的是系统自带的ssh服务，不像ftp还需要额外的进行安装。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>LNMP环境搭建</title><link>/post/lnmp%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</link><pubDate>Sun, 11 Apr 2021 16:29:03 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/lnmp%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</guid><description>&lt;p>Linux+Nginx+MySQL+PHP&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Awk</title><link>/post/awk/</link><pubDate>Sun, 11 Apr 2021 16:26:20 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/awk/</guid><description>&lt;p>awk有多个不同版本的演化：awk-&amp;gt;nawk-&amp;gt;mawk-&amp;gt;gawk&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Linux Shell Bash</title><link>/post/linux-shell-bash/</link><pubDate>Thu, 08 Apr 2021 17:12:50 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/linux-shell-bash/</guid><description>&lt;p>shell bash 脚本相关&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Linux Systemd</title><link>/post/linux-systemd/</link><pubDate>Thu, 08 Apr 2021 17:07:04 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/linux-systemd/</guid><description>&lt;p>systemd 是一个专用于 Linux 操作系统的系统与服务管理器。 当作为启动进程(PID=1)运行时， 它将作为初始化系统运行， 也就是启动并维护各种用户空间的服务。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Linux Iproute2 Ss</title><link>/post/linux-iproute2-ss/</link><pubDate>Thu, 08 Apr 2021 17:03:27 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/linux-iproute2-ss/</guid><description>&lt;p>ss命令可以用来获取socket统计信息，它可以显示和netstat类似的内容。但ss的优势在于它能够显示更多更详细的有关TCP和连接状态的信息，而且比netstat更快速更高效。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Linux Iproute2 Ip</title><link>/post/linux-iproute2-ip/</link><pubDate>Thu, 08 Apr 2021 17:00:27 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/linux-iproute2-ip/</guid><description>&lt;p>iproute2是Linux网络工具包，它代替了net-tools（ifconfig，vconfig，route，arp等）。ip是iproute2中的一个命令之一。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Linux Date日期时间</title><link>/post/linux-date%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/</link><pubDate>Thu, 08 Apr 2021 16:49:44 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/linux-date%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%9F%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/</guid><description>&lt;p>Linux 的日期时间管理&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Crontab</title><link>/post/crontab/</link><pubDate>Thu, 08 Apr 2021 15:09:38 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/crontab/</guid><description>&lt;p>Linux定时任务。crontab提交和管理用户的需要周期性执行的任务&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Sed命令</title><link>/post/sed%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Feb 2021 20:40:20 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/sed%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4/</guid><description>&lt;p>Linux sed命令, 用于处理文本&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>